commits.message:
Disable URLEndpointListenerTest.TestStatus

Disable URLEndpointListenerTest.TestStatus as it could run forever.

Do not validate connection count in ValidateMultipleReplication

Do not validate connection count in ValidateMultipleReplication as there are no reliable ways to get the connection count especially the active connection counts by polling. This is a source of flaky tests. Also there is already a specific test that tests this.
